name: Neko Dansu Party
description:
Neko Dansu Party is a love letter for Japanese Arcade, Rhythm Game, and also Love for Cats. Play with your Keyboard Arrow and let's get the party started!

Programmer & Game Designer: Muhammad Ardhan Fadhlurrahman

Visual Artist: Muhammad Akmal Khairurrahman

20/11/2022: this version only had one song, next update would included more song.
